## Tip Calculator
print("Welcome to the tip calculator")
bill_amount=float(input("What was the total bill amount ?\n"))
tip_value=int(input("How much tip would you like to give? : 10, 12, 15\n" ) )
no_of_people=int(input("How many people to split the bill?\n" ) )

total_bill=bill_amount+((bill_amount*tip_value)/100)


tip=total_bill/no_of_people

print(f"Each person should pay : ${tip}.")
